surveyproformat_label.content:
This is a demo survey I made to let you quickly see some features of the items. This not a real survey, question are silly or non complete or meaningless (and, for sure, written in a bad English), but they are examples of what you can get playing with this module.

I divided this survey in several pages. Each page is focused on a specific field element.
The four format elements are used here and there on needs.

Of course you can even submit a survey... but I do not think you will never get a good outcome from its analysis. :-)

Enjoy your browsing.
